\b Running the Gel \
\pard\pardeftab720\ri0\sl278

\b0 \cf0 Make up 15% denaturing PAGE gel (UreaGel-SequaGel-System, National Diagnostics). For most applications we use medium thickness spacers (0.8mm) with 19.5 cm\super 2\nosupersub  large glass plate and 19.5 cm x 16 cm small plate and a comb with well volumes of ~30 \'b5l (LABREPCO). Clean plates, spacers and comb thoroughly and dry. Plates can be silanized if desired.\
\
15% PAGE \'96 30 mL from Sequagel Mix (enough for 1 gel):
